name: Hatsuse Izuna
desc: A cute foxgirl trying to take over Discord

name: Satania Dropout
desc: Do you believe in our lord Satania? Are you devilish enough to put bottles in the recycling bin with the cap on? Are you afraid of all the mean dogs that keep stealing your Melon Bread? If so, then come join Satania Dropout, every day we praise Satania and we protect her from the evil bullis, help us getting Satania to rule the world!

name: JukeBot
desc: JukeBot offers stable, high quality music for your server supporting various sources such as SoundCloud and YouTube, with over 18,000 servers!

name: NekoTony
desc: NekoTony is a world renowned coder or in this server anyways. With bots to code and a life of his, you'll sure enjoy the server. With over 1k people and fun events, be sure to join.

name: Kitsuchan
desc: Kitsuchan is a bot that does many things and is here to make your guild more fun! She's not finished yet and may have bugs, but is (mostly) in servicable order.

name: Discord Cards
desc: Discord Cards is a trading card discord bot where you can buy and open card packs, recieve daily currency, craft badges, trade with friends and so on! Also featuring trading, a global market, clubs, badges and multi-language support!

name: Birb
desc: Birb is a discord bot jam-packed with all the cool features that all Discord bots should have and all that you could ever want!

name: Discord Hub
desc: We want to give new users and server owners a place to get the support, resources, and help they need to succeed in the world of Discord with guides, support, resources, and advice!

name: Discord Dungeons
desc: Discord Dungeons is a place where you can play a text-based RPG. Fit with Items, events, global market, adventure, quests, guilds, armor, rings and more!

name: PikaGirl
desc: PikaGirl is a fun, advanced Discord Bot that is sure to rock your server. It comes with countless commands and so many features that it will make your head spin! Add her to your server today and get started!

name: Our Anime Quest
desc: Our Anime Quest is a server dedicated to gamers and anime lovers of all sorts! We accept anyone that wishes to join! If you are interested, the invite link is below!
